 * Initial revision.
 * Two DIPAGB test examples with inverse lexicographical term order INVLEX.
 * A comparison of the normal strategy and the normal with sugar strategy
 *                 with variable weight list (0,...,0) and (1,...,1) in DIPAGB
 *          and of the functions DIPAGB and DIIFGB/DIPGB.
 *
 * ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
